01:13:54.410 --> 01:13:59.090
I want the matrix
n, n, n, n, 0, 0.

01:13:59.090 --> 01:14:00.590
So j equals k.

01:14:00.590 --> 01:14:01.510
That's the diagonal.

01:14:01.510 --> 01:14:04.240
That's where I want to get n,
