01:15:56.080 --> 01:15:59.315
AUDIENCE: That's
the e to the i tau--

01:15:59.315 --> 01:16:00.190
ERIK DEMAINE: Just z.

01:16:00.190 --> 01:16:03.295
ERIK DEMAINE: Oh,
